data.description: Home improvements over the past year totaling over $80k including 2 new HVAC systems, lighting fixtures throughout just to name a few. Too many to list, no detail has been overlooked. This home combines elegance with comfortable living, a perfect retreat for families. Situated on a spacious .311 acre lot offering a sense of privacy and tranquility. This home boasts a generous floor plan with an abundance of natural light and plantation shutters. A well-designed layout seamlessly connects the living spaces. Gourmet kitchen, ss appliances, granite countertops, and ample storage. Fall in love with the hand scraped hardwood floors and travertine in the kitchen. Master suite features a spa-like bathroom, walk-in closet with access to the laundry room. Enjoy the ultimate entertainment exp in the media-game room. The home office provides a quiet and inspiring space for remote work. This property extends its luxury with a meticulously landscaped yard, saltwater pool and spa and covered patio.
